Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hercules.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:02:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah bilang, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.67,0:03:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Alat tidak bisa melampaui batasnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dia bersinar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar sialan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.72,0:03:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau lupa tersenyum,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Temanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau amat menyedihkan, All Might.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.62,0:03:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau kehilangan senyumanmu, harapanmu,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan kau merangkak di tanah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.92,0:03:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}terpelintir oleh keputusasaan\Ndan rasa sakit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.51,0:03:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, aku akan membuatmu hancur\Ndan tak berdaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti yang dulu kau lakukan padaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tubuhku tidak bisa bergerak!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.10,0:03:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Darah kita
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.44,0:03:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sama-sama berwarna merah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa kau?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Habisi dia,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.16,0:04:11.20,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}All Might!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.29,0:04:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Akhirnya terhubung!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kalian berdua baik-baik saja, 'kan?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.46,0:04:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}All Might?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Waktu kita sedikit. Jadi, langsung saja.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kalian harus bergegas ke Gunga\Nsekarang juga.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Jika ada yang bisa\Nmenghentikan krisis di Gunga,{\i0}
