Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.63,0:05:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}All Might. Ya, All Might.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.22,0:05:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kau bisa mengerti, 'kan?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Alasanku mengekspos diriku seperti ini?{\i0}
